featured_reviews.review_id:
The masjid is big and beautiful.
A large no. Of muslims can offer their salah here.
The place is clean and it is not situated in a congested place.
The roads are wide enough to have 2 cars per lane.
The only problem is that there's no place for car parking one can park their two wheeler inside of the mosque.
